Shopping in central London can be a nightmare - and never more so than during the festive season.

But department store giant Selfridges have launched a bespoke shopping service to take the stress out of Christmas shopping. Meet Selfridges' 'Elfridges: the band of helpful elves dispersed around the Oxford Street store to make present purchasing more pleasant.

They will help shoppers with almost
everything, whether it's finding the perfect present, flagging down a 
taxi or gift-wrapping your purchases.

These aren't just any elves, they are Selfridges Christmas 'Elfridges, dressed head-to-toe is designer gear

